-10c3af85ad2fc722e1c22f836270c6b8_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7aa92c050c2f5a1561b52b7308bbe5ce_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7aa92c050c2f5a1561b52b7308bbe5ce_r.jpg&quot;&gt;小孩床在摇动？No！是他自己在抽搐……&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;小孩力量大增？不，这只是不小心打通了任督二脉，成为了绝世高手：&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3e56dfeab9285a2730ddd847aa1ddc58_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3e56dfeab9285a2730ddd847aa1ddc58_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f17e1476ebe3698ef39eee2ae2fd35ae_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f17e1476ebe3698ef39eee2ae2fd35ae_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9c20a37df9ef4daa3c6be96bebb299b1_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9c20a37df9ef4daa3c6be96bebb299b1_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6c96465fd6d93a1e5d7cb4e2c2a39f46_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6c96465fd6d93a1e5d7cb4e2c2a39f46_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cd55aca9e0f197d409b177726b4192a6_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cd55aca9e0f197d409b177726b4192a6_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a2b34ec2c261b3c3d34738c16eaadd2e_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a2b34ec2c261b3c3d34738c16eaadd2e_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;他也不是胡诌，还专门做了试验：&lt;br&gt;就是下面这个&lt;b&gt;“通灵神器”&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3311c8bf2a4fbe089fc29c2cc8a99231_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3311c8bf2a4fbe089fc29c2cc8a99231_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d2eeeaf283e2fe3464ca6c00bb8d90eb_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d2eeeaf283e2fe3464ca6c00bb8d90eb_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b42261b4d10e3bba17a289b05f18f95f_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b42261b4d10e3bba17a289b05f18f95f_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;简单来说，就是被电一下：&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-232970c2fda63863b84a6adb9ffbaf1a_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;616&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;347&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;616&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-232970c2fda63863b84a6adb9ffbaf1a_r.jpg&quot;&gt;说到这里，想到了永信大师：&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-cc64a0cf2ff2b2b4dbea046f62698b81_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;315&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;614&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;315&quot;&gt;阿弥陀佛，罪过罪过，是这一位永信“大师”：&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.