0000;font-weight: bold;">【10400毫安移动电源】+【VR魔镜】+<span style="color: #ff0000;font-size: 22.0px;font-weight: bold;line-height: 33.0px;white-space: pre-wrap;">【小米活塞耳机】+</span>【线控自拍杆】+【钢化膜*2】+【透明清水壳】+【木质支架】+【延保1年】</span> </p><p><span style="font-size: 22.0px;font-weight: bold;">5、产品基本参数：</span> </p><p><span style="font-size: 22.0px;">①全网通4G+双卡盲插，双卡双待；</span> </p><p><span style="font-size: 22.0px;">②金属机身，mTouch指纹识别，支付宝/微信指纹支付；</span> </p><p><span style="font-size: 22.0px;">③5.5英寸2.5D1080P夏普屏；</span> </p><p><span style="font-size: 22.0px;">④mCharge安全快充功能，双频WIFI；</span> </p><p><span style="font-size: 22.0px;">⑤4+32G/3+32G大内存，A72架构10核处理器；</span> </p><p><span style="font-size: 22.0px;">⑥6P镜头，索尼IMX386 CMOS，1200万像素；</span> </p><p><span style="font-size: 22.0px;">以上为魅族MX6基本参数，具体以官方发布为准，如有错误欢迎纠正。</span> </p><p><span style="font-family: kaiti_gb2312;"><span style="font-size: 18.0px;"><img alt="MX6参数图.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170120/1484903902162660.jpg" class="img-ks-lazyload"/><img alt="实拍照片-红色.jpg" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170120/1484903903141918.jpg" class="img-ks-lazyload"/><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170120/1484903903916404.jpg" class="img-ks-lazyload"/><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170120/1484903903233318.jpg" class="img-ks-lazyload"/></span></span> </p><table style="width: 569px;" width="790"><tbody><tr style="margin: 0.0px;padding: 0.0px;" class="firstRow"><td style="border-color: #000000;color: #ffffff;font-weight: bold;" width="100"><span style="margin: 0.0px;padding: 0.0px;">套餐</span> </td><td style="border-color: #000000;color: #ffffff;font-weight: bold;" width="0"><span style="margin: 0.0px;padding: 0.0px;">详情</span> </td><td style="border-color: #000000;color: #ffffff;font-weight: bold;" width="100"><span style="margin: 0.0px;padding: 0.0px;">价格</span> </td></tr><tr style="margin: 0.0px;padding: 0.0px;"><td style="border-color: #000000;font-weight: bold;color: #555555;" width="0"><span style="margin: 0.0px;padding: 0.0px;">官方标配</